So you think that he's hiding
something behind it.

00:09:01.755 --> 00:09:02.070
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:09:02.070 --> 00:09:03.750
ADAM GRANT: Maybe All right,
that's reasonable.

00:09:03.750 --> 00:09:05.890
Some people also look to this
smile and say he's baring his

00:09:05.890 --> 00:09:07.040
teeth, and in the
animal kingdom

00:09:07.040 --> 00:09:08.170
